     2  *>****************************************************************
     3  *>               Print one 940 Form on plain paper               *
     4  *>                                                               *
     5  *>     This program computes RI - Rhode Island tax at section    *
     6  *>      19 of the report - Should it not be in their State tax   *
     7  *>       table  instead ?                                        *
     8  *>      If so see code at                                        *
     9  *>    RD - "19 Rhode Island Portion of 15c                       *
    10  *>   and   code at arounbd 608 starting with :                   *
    11  *>      if       PY-PR1-Co-State = "RI"                          *
    12  *>                 move     WS-Tot-Taxable-Futa to WS-RI-Tax     *
    13  *>      etc.                                                     *
    14  *>                                                               *
    15  *>   Temp program name may be py210 - coding from print940       *
    16  *>                                                               *
    17  *>    Prograam uses RW - Report Writer.                          *
    18  *>                                                               *
    19  *>****************************************************************
