    55  *> 08/03/2026 vbc - 1.0.00 Coding starting.
    56  *>                         After testing version will be set to v3.3.
    57  *>                         WARNING: You MUST set the terminal program to be 80
    58  *>                         cols wide and MORE than 25 lines deep and this is to
    59  *>                         allow for the some of the extra lines beyond 24 to
    60  *>                         be used as areas for the warning or error messages
    61  *>                         to be displayed. 26 lines is the minimum.
    62  *>                         This procedure must be applied at all times when
    63  *>                         running Payroll.
    64  *>                         For almost all terminal programs, can be achieved
    65  *>                         by pulling the left and bottom edges of the terminal
    66  *>                         screen with the mouse and holding right button and
    67  *>                         pulling until the correct number is displayed, and
    68  *>                         doing so, one at a time or pulling bottom right
    69  *>                         corner.
    70  *> 11/03/2026 vbc -        Coding Completed.
