  1647                display  PY586 at line WS-23-Lines col 1 foreground-color 6 erase eos
  1648                display  SY001 at line WS-Lines    col 1
  1649                accept   WS-Reply at line WS-Lines col 48 AUTO
  1650                close    PY-Param1-File
