  1762   ZZ040-Evaluate-Message      Section.
  1763  *>**********************************
  1764  *>
  1765  *> For PY-PR1 parameter file anfd other using PR-PR1-Status.
  1766  *>
  1767  *>C      copy "FileStat-Msgs-2.cpy" replacing MSG    by WS-Eval-Msg
  1768  *>C                                         STATUS by PY-PR1-Status.
  1769  *> ***************************************************************
  1770  *> ** Author: Gary L. Cutler                                    **
  1771  *> **         CutlerGL@gmail.com                                **
  1772  *> ** Amendments Vincent B. Coen                                **
  1773  *> **         vbcoen@gmail.com                                  **
  1774  *> **                                                           **
  1775  *> ** This copybook defines an EVALUATE statement capable of    **
  1776  *> ** translating two-digit FILE-STATUS codes to a message.     **
  1777  *> **                                                           **
  1778  *> ** Use the REPLACING option to COPY to change the names of   **
  1779  *> ** the MSG and STATUS identifiers to                         **
  1780  *> ** the names your program needs.                             **
  1781  *> Such as replacing STATUS by fs-reply msg by exception-msg.   **
  1782  *>                                                              **
ACS Cobol Xref v2.03.18          Dictionary File for PRINT940    11/03/2026  21:58:11:51                               Page   34

  1783  *> ** chg 09/08/23 vbc for missing statuses                     **
  1784  *> ** Chg 11/12/23 vbc for missing statuses                     **
  1785  *> ** Chg 10/04/25 vbc match all quotes & spacing/layout        **
  1786  *> ** chg to FREE format                                        **
  1787  *> ** Chg 24/08/25 vbc #91 description.                         **
  1788  *> ** Chg 15.11.25 vbc Replace all ' for "                      **
  1789  *> ***************************************************************
  1790  *>
  1791   EVALUATE PY-PR1-Status
  1792   WHEN "00" MOVE "Success                  " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1793   WHEN "02" MOVE "Success Duplicate        " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1794   WHEN "04" MOVE "Success Incomplete       " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1795   WHEN "05" MOVE "Success Optional, Missing" TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1796   when "06" move "Multiple Records LS      " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1797   WHEN "07" MOVE "Success No Unit          " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1798   when "09" move "Success LS Bad Data      " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1799   WHEN "10" MOVE "End Of File              " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1800   WHEN "14" MOVE "Out Of Key Range         " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1801   WHEN "21" MOVE "Key Invalid              " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1802   WHEN "22" MOVE "Key Exists               " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1803   WHEN "23" MOVE "Key Not Exists           " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1804   WHEN "24" MOVE "Key Boundary violation   " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1805   WHEN "30" MOVE "Permanent Error          " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1806   WHEN "31" MOVE "Inconsistent Filename    " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1807   WHEN "34" MOVE "Boundary Violation       " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1808   WHEN "35" MOVE "File Not Found           " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1809   WHEN "37" MOVE "Permission Denied        " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1810   WHEN "38" MOVE "Closed With Lock         " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1811   WHEN "39" MOVE "Conflict Attribute       " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1812   WHEN "41" MOVE "Already Open             " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1813   WHEN "42" MOVE "Not Open                 " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1814   WHEN "43" MOVE "Read Not Done            " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1815   WHEN "44" MOVE "Record Overflow          " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1816   WHEN "46" MOVE "Read Error               " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1817   WHEN "47" MOVE "Input Denied             " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1818   WHEN "48" MOVE "Output Denied            " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1819   WHEN "49" MOVE "I/O Denied               " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1820   WHEN "51" MOVE "Record Locked            " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1821   WHEN "52" MOVE "End-Of-Page              " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1822   WHEN "57" MOVE "I/O Linage               " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1823   WHEN "61" MOVE "File Sharing Failure     " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1824   WHEN "71" MOVE "Bad Character LS         " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1825   WHEN "91" MOVE "Feature Not Available    " TO WS-Eval-Msg
  1826            WHEN OTHER
  1827   MOVE "Unknown File PY-PR1-Status      " TO WS-
  1828  *>
  1829       END-EVALUATE.
  1830
  1831  *>>W Msg29 Caution: One or more replacing sources not found
  1832  *>
  1833   ZZ040-Eval-Msg-Exit.
  1834       exit     section.
  1835  *>
